This is caused by hard-coded name[1] in BTF_ID_LIST_GLOBAL (w/o
CONFIG_DEBUG_INFO_BTF). Fix this by adding a parameter n to
BTF_ID_LIST_GLOBAL. This avoids ifdef CONFIG_DEBUG_INFO_BTF in btf.c and
filter.c.

